"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423834","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2015-11-05","<p>I refer the hon. Member to the answer given by the Economic Secretary to the Treasury, my hon. Friend the Member for West Worcestershire on 2 November 2015 to Question UIN <a href="http://www.parliament.uk/business/publications/written-questions-answers-statements/written-question/Commons/2015-10-26/13524/" target="_blank">13524</a>.</p>","Broxtowe","Anna Soubry",,"2015-11-05T15:23:44.047Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423834/answer","Biography information for Anna Soubry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423834/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/423834/answer",,,,,,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2015-10-26","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills: Credit Unions","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, what steps he is taking to promote the use of credit unions in the work of his Department; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Gareth Thomas","Harrow West","Gareth Thomas","13502"
